{"tid":672864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： Madam翁倫敦狙擊　 假和尚即脫袈裟「改邪歸正」","createTime":"2018-05-21T10:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T02:41:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3c10997e603ba7e58b36b115d416b1c170f603","tid":672864,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:59:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397161&d=udWQ8CAbBnyBdUhumdbJwDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=f2ec0039\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397161&h=42a215db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397161</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\nMadam翁倫敦狙擊　<br />\n假和尚即脫袈裟「改邪歸正」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/a1203a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2Fa1203a.gif&h=c9f4cd25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Madam翁令假和尚即場脫掉袈裟，對方仲承諾「改邪歸正」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為踢爆假和尚不遺餘力嘅「Madam翁」翁靜晶，同假和尚似乎特別「有緣」，估唔到去到英國倫敦都遇上，一如在港即場大踢爆，仲「感化」埋假和尚。<br />\n<br />\n翁靜晶星期六凌晨喺「佛門警訊 Buddhist Alert」群組上載短片，話喺16日一落機就見到假和尚喺街頭行騙，片中一名身穿和尚服裝男子正向外籍途人索求金錢，Madam翁即刻喝止。<br />\n<br />\n隨後Madam翁向對方表明專門捉假和尚，追問佢嚟自邊度同有冇戒碟。假和尚最初只係重申冇呃人等，又攞出黃紙紅字紙符，點知Madam翁踢爆「你知道佛陀說不能用符咒，你不是真的和尚，我叫警察來」，又叫對方念大悲咒，但對方只識答「大悲咒就是大慈大悲」。<br />\n<br />\nMadam翁仲要求對方脫掉袈裟，否則報警處理，對方最終脫下並承諾不會再穿袈裟騙人，Madam翁又贏一仗嘞。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 至抵精明鼠巡百佳　 識揀收爐燒味<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片： 蜘蛛叔飛躍10樓外牆整冷氣"},{"pid":"78770b12ef0b7894bbb1460fc691a2847281c840","tid":672864,"uid":93479,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"羅漢托世下凡伏妖"},{"pid":"6109134fb061aaaab78e89e312f1a2bcd6066cde","tid":672864,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"佢唔驚倫敦蒙難記係一百年後再發生係佢身上? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc285b9d5b5fbefcba4470d0577a93f076e06b4","tid":672864,"uid":51121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"如果連登仔有佢一成水平 何愁大事不成"},{"pid":"515575df54df71a73029bb5efdef10447a02f94c","tid":672864,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:29:04.000Z","msg":"屌你毒果妓者, <br />\n<br />\nLady 翁呀<br />\n<br />\nMa乜撚dam, 都唔怕笑死人"},{"pid":"aebb8686c7b39ca7366642d8952201d6e41dff1f","tid":672864,"uid":42453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78770b12ef0b7894bbb1460fc691a2847281c840","tid":672864,"uid":93479,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"羅漢托世下凡伏妖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"你估做戲咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/104020_228ef4dc1254fb9092d5c254673f1133.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F104020_228ef4dc1254fb9092d5c254673f1133.png&h=af806719&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}